     specifications  or  create  new  ones in order to set up the
     "current" specifications within PROREP.  Changes, additions,
     and  deletions  affect  current  specifications.   No  saved
     report specification files are altered until the user  saves
     the  current  data.   A  series  of  simple,  yet  powerful,
     commands allow the user to control the  interactive  editing
