     heading,  except  that  the  column heading must precede the
     options.


     3.  *ROWS

          Up to 100 rows, 15 characters each.  Blank row headings
     are  permitted  in  all  but the last row.  There must be at
     least one row defined.

          The row heading can  be  followed  by  any  of  several
     options,  enclosed  in angle brackets <>.  These row options
     are always overridden by  column  options  if  both  are  in
