     shown  above,  R(3)  will  be  directly related to the newly
     calculated value of R(1)  rather  than  the  value  of  R(1)
     passed from the last period.

          Throughout  the  entire  process  of  forecasting  each
     column of the output report via the "period rules", the data
     variables  are  updated  automatically  by   PROFILE.    For

