               character   after  the  sequence  number  will  be
               ignored.

             - Response files may not  reference  other  response
               files.

             - Response  files  can  be  opened  by  one  PROFILE
               program  (i.e.   PROFILE,  PROREP, or PRODEP), and
               can transfer control to any other program  without
               interruption.


